data.description: Comfortable 3 bedroom & 2 bath ranch home located in the highly sought after Turtle Cove on a level private lot with plenty of green space in the back yard for privacy & also has an FHA assumable mortgage!! Just minutes from the lake this home features a new roof, new LVP flooring in the main living areas, kitchen and bathrooms, new water heater, split floor plan, spacious bedrooms, owner's suite with a roomy walk-in closet & open living room space with wood burning fireplace. Outside includes a large driveway with room to park the boat/RV, private deck overlooking your private wooded back yard and covered front porch. Home also includes a transferrable Home Warranty. Turtle Cove is an amazing community that features a golf course, clubhouse with full restaurant & bar, large partially covered pool, tennis, pickleball courts & white sand beaches with 3 boat ramps.
